description:
LA, along a humid motorway lit by the red neon of strip clubs.
London, a gorgeous and wild brunette, arrives. Erotic dancer in a club, she remembers the particular night when she was struck by her desire for another dancer, Dylan Ryan, a tall sculpted blond who knows exactly what she wants and how she wants it.
She's haunted by hallucinated flashbacks of their fevered nights at the clandestine and muggy Strap-on Motel. The chemical reaction of their bodies is explosive, and their desire insatiable. Their mouths devour each other as their burning hot caresses lead them to explore every page of the lesbian kama sutra -- spiced with dildos.
Strap-on lesbian sex will never die.
title: Strap-on Motel
